author: IGN
description:
Take a look at the Operation Blackout Gameplay Announcement Trailer for Delta Force, a free-to-play first-person online shooter developed by Team Jade. Players will be able to interface with the game in an all-new way with Operation Blackout which sets out to bring nighttime combat to the game. Engage in intense firefights in the dead of night enabling the use of night-vision goggles to be crucial for success. Operation Blackout is coming to Delta Force with the new Eclipse Vigil Season launching on April 21 for PC.

#DeltaForce #OperationBlackout #Gaming
title: Delta Force - Official Operation Blackout Gameplay Announcement Trailer

Take a look at the Cinematic Short Story Trailer for Marathon, a sci-fi team-based extraction shooter developed by Bungie. Don't miss this glimpse at the narrative and mystery behind the world of Marathon as players strive to unravel the secrets that lie dormant. Marathon is launching on September 23 for PlayStation 5 (PS5), Xbox Series X|S, and PC (Steam).

description:
Take a look at the Features Trailer for Lunar Remastered Collection, a remastered bundle with both Lunar: Silver Star Complete and Lunar 2: Eternal Blue Complete for modern platforms. Check out the latest trailer to see the new features of the collection including enhanced graphics, Japanese and English voice options, quality-of-life features, and more. The Lunar Remastered Collection is launching on April 18 for PlayStation 4 (PS4), Xbox One, Nintendo Switch, and PC (Steam).

#LunarRemasteredCollection #Gaming #IGN
title: Lunar Remastered Collection - Official Features Trailer

author: IGN
description:
Don't miss the Xbox Announcement Trailer for Zenless Zone Zero, an urban fantasy action RPG developed by HoYoverse. Players will be able to fight and engage with the game's flashy and stylish combat on the Xbox platform and claim a platform-exclusive title, The Xenless. Zenless Zone Zero is launching on Xbox in June 2025 with the game being available now for PlayStation 5 (PS5), iOS, Android, and PC.

#ZenlessZoneZero #Xbox #Gaming
title: Zenless Zone Zero - Official Xbox Announcement Trailer

author: IGN
description:
Take a look at the 'Safest City in the World’ Trailer for MindsEye, a third-person action-adventure game developed by Build A Rocket Boy. Players can get a sense of the game's main setting of Redrock, the self-proclaimed safest city in the world. The city is fitted with a computerized law enforcement system, state-of-the-art entertainment, revolutionary transportation, and more. Visit Redrock in MindsEye, launching on June 10 for PlayStation 5 (PS5), Xbox Series X|S, and PC (Steam and Epic Games Store).

#MindsEye #Gaming #IGN
title: MindsEye - Official ‘Safest City in the World’ Trailer
